<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Project</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles */
        body, h1, h2, p {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Global styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Header styles */
        .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Main content styles */
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* About Me section styles */
        .about-me {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .about-me img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* Diagram placeholder styles */
        .diagram-placeholder {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            /* Add your diagram here using an <img> or <object> tag */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Project</h1>
        <p>Using Jenkins, Docker, and .NET for Web Applications</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <div class="about-me">
                <img src="https://static.businessworld.in/article/article_extra_large_image/1608109167_bnsMKG_Nagarro_Vertical_Dark.png" alt="Parvesh's Image">
                <p>I am Parvesh, a Software Engineer at Nagarro.</p>
            </div>

            <h2>About This Project</h2>
            <p>This project is a combination of Docker, Jenkins, and a .NET web application. It leverages modern technologies to build robust web applications efficiently.</p>
            <p><strong>How it works:</strong></p>
            <ol>
                <li>We use Jenkins to automate our pipeline.</li>
                <li>Docker is utilized to build and run the .NET web application.</li>
                <li>Git repositories hold the source code, with changes triggering Jenkins pipelines.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Explore the documentation on <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/aspnet/core" target="_blank">building Web apps with ASP.NET Core</a> to get started.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Diagram Placeholder -->
        <div class="diagram-placeholder">
            <!-- Add your diagram here using an <img> or <object> tag -->
            <!-- Example: <img src="your-diagram-image.jpg" alt="Diagram"> -->
        </div>
    </div>
